    "description": "The world is in crisis! A woman is enjoying a slice of pizza. A man is marrying the person he loves. A child has set up a lemonade stand across the street! The problem? All of it pisses you off! <br><br>Take control of Tyler Tactics in this highly-replayable, action-arcade comedy game. Outsmart your foes with hundreds of unique tactics and bring them to political, financial, and emotional ruin! Lie to the public, steal candy from a baby, unleash the power of the universe itself! Nothing is off limits in this absurd comedy adventure from Bomb Sequitur Games!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>7 hilarious levels<br></li><li>6 unique minigames<br></li><li>386 unique tactics, supers, and fails!<br></li><li>8 Hand drawn cutscenes<br></li><li>12 original songs<br></li><li>3 difficulties for increased replayability<br></li><li>Over 25,000 words</li></ul>",
